description.en: KITTEE Token is a TRC-20 MEME token on the Tron Network. It is tradable on SouthXChange under the symbol KTE and paired with BTC, USDT, and TRX. You can find it by searching for KTE and you will see KTE/BTC, KTE/USDT, KTE/TRX.
